title: Seahawks party barge adrift in Puget Sound
text:
A Seahawks-themed party barge was spotted adrift in Puget Sound Friday morning.
The Coast Guard said it appears to be a tent trailer on some sort of barge that likely broke free north of Blake Island.
No one is on the barge.
Chopper 7 was over the scene where a Coast Guard boat was responding.
